==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quadruplicate
<hw>Quad*ru"pli*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Quadruplicated</conjf>
<pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Quadruplicating</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>quadruplicatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>quadruplicare</ets>, fr.
<ets>quadruple</ets><?/ fourfold. See <er>Quadruplex</er>.]</ety>
<def>To make fourfold; to double twice; to quadruple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadruplicate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Quadruplicate
<hw>Quad*ru"pli*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quadruplicatus</ets>, p. p.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Fourfold; doubled twice; four times repeated;
<as>as, a <ex>quadruplicate</ex> ratio, or a <ex>quadruplicate</ex>
proportion</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>Raised to the fourth power.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadruplication</ent>⟦br⟧
